data.text:
Construction of a new rental apartment complex located in southeast Edmonton, in the neighborhood of Tamarack (Aster). Building 1 will feature 174 units over an underground parkade. The entire development will include 347 units between the two buildings.

The City of Edmonton issued a building permit for the building on October 3, 2022.
